Class StatusBarFeatures

  • java.lang.Object
    • controls.StatusBarFeatures

  • public class StatusBarFeatures
extends java.lang.Object
    Class StatusBarFeatures represents part on the status bar (last part) displaying check boxes providing special features (display of street names and street congestion levels).
    Author:
    Michal Rein, Ondřej Motyčka
